{"tid":1486210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"I love you 3000","createTime":"2019-08-18T20:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T22:39:42.000Z","uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23c79706946487636aed8d76862199f285033ff5","tid":1486210,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnjR7Jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnjR7Jp.jpg&h=dd1c3fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBaby, take my hand<br />\nI want you to be my wife"},{"pid":"1cb5b424c710bdff5e283c53aff72dcd93e4c64b","tid":1486210,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:23:56.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSssWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=317381ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSssWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=317381ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"90aeade3ae2c181bb57cbf265cf186a2eb5196e7","tid":1486210,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D3zk39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D3zk39.jpg&h=585fae14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCos ur my Ariel<br />\nAnd i love u 3000"},{"pid":"3e8acd96acfa8fe41a44803c14084709887f7339","tid":1486210,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsDGLAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsDGLAr.jpg&h=b22e5b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBaby, take a chance<br />\nCos i want this to be something<br />\nStraight out of a disney movie"},{"pid":"019a6217a66f4f82d38d3e28d6a06706fd46edda","tid":1486210,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislik